      Fields in com.projetloki.genesis declared as TimingFunction 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static TimingFunction TimingFunction.EASE
      Similar to ease-in-out, but accelerates more sharply at the beginning and the acceleration already starts to slow down near the middle of it.
      static TimingFunction TimingFunction.EASE_IN
      Begins slowly, then progressively accelerates until the final state is reached and the animation stops abruptly.
      static TimingFunction TimingFunction.EASE_IN_OUT
      Starts slowly, accelerates than slows down when approaching to its final state.
      static TimingFunction TimingFunction.EASE_OUT
      Starts quickly then slow progressively down when approaching to its final state.
      static TimingFunction TimingFunction.LINEAR
      The animation goes from its initial state to its final state with constant speed.
